{"product_id":"rhubarb-shampoo-with-aloe-extract-250-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Shampoo With Rhubarb Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/auhinnad-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2022\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour hair is ready for invigoration. Indulge it with spring-like freshness, gloss, and shine!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe juicy rhubarb-enriched shampoo is designed for intensive enlivening of dry and damaged hair. The extra moisturising aloe extract with Pro-Vitamin B5 restores, nurtures, and reinforces the damaged hair structure. The vitamin treatment that your hair needs.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters, Citric Acid, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract*, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Parfum, Panthenol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,57%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulfate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e| alcohol-free |\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927708479815,"sku":"","price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-250ml-1916309.png?v=1763665704","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/rhubarb-shampoo-with-aloe-extract-250-ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}